## Acceptance Tests

### Test 1: Successful Explicit L0 Inclusion
```python
def test_explicit_l0_in_context_pack():
    """L0 chunk requested by ID appears in assembled pack."""
    # Setup: create valid L0 record in store
    l0_id = create_test_l0_chunk(
        chunk_id="test-chunk-001",
        citation_id="TEST-DOC",
        summary="Test L0 summary content"
    )
    
    # Request pack with explicit L0
    pack = assemble_context_pack(
        request=ContextPackRequest(explicit_l0_ids=[l0_id])
    )
    
    # Assert
    assert any(item.item_type == ContextItemType.L0_CHUNK for item in pack.items)
    l0_item = next(i for i in pack.items if i.item_id == l0_id)
    assert "test-chunk-001" in l0_item.content
    assert l0_item.inclusion_reason == "explicit_request"
```

